.NET Core 1.0.name: IDiscordGateway
.NET Core 1.0.summary: Provides interaction with the Discord gateway API.

methods.name: ConnectToVoice(DiscordGuildChannel channel)
methods.summary: Creates a voice connection to the specified DiscordGuildChannel.
methods.returns: The voice client interface for the created connection.

params.value: The guild voice channel to connect to.

methods.name: DisconnectFromVoice(DiscordGuild guild)
methods.summary: Disconnects the DiscordVoiceClient currently connected to the specified DiscordGuild.
